I see this problem when using [`SearchDelegate`](https://api.flutter.dev/flutter/material/SearchDelegate-class.html) and entering text using my physical keyboard with [Vysor](https://www.vysor.io/). Pressing the keyboard keys on screen or with the mouse on the mirrored keyboard on the computer works. 

The problem is, that the input after the messages are shown gets completely stuck. No input neither with the physical nor virtual keyboard is possible until the screen is reloaded. 

```
